cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR 

This paper is likely to belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) sub-category as it deals with object detection and pose estimation in an industrial context. Computer Vision (cs.CV) is also a likely sub-category as it involves the use of point pair features for object detection. Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) are also possible sub-categories as the paper proposes a new method for generating synthetic datasets and introduces a heuristic method to reduce computational complexity. Finally, Graphics (cs.GR) is a possible sub-category as the paper discusses the presence of self-similar features in the application.
